room_title: Escape room "The Elevator" by Hellscream Room Escapes in Colorado Springs
room_address: 3021 N. Hancock Ave, Colorado Springs, CO 80907
room_description:
Did you know there is an elevator in Dr. VonHellton's manor? Well, the good Dr. would like you to come test out his experimental lift and provide your feedback. Your first test: figure out how to make The Elevator work! Your second test: escape!
You can choose a non-scary version of the game.
